 dividing line are discussed first. Hl cannot be rejected. 
 This points to/shows that small and large farms have equal 
 relative money-based (wasting very little while working or producing something). H2 is rejected, suggesting that differences exist in the relative price (wasting very little while working or producing something) between small and large farms. H3 is re- 
 
